summary: Amadeus's Bday by krystalfan-2 I literally forgot how to draw my own characters, in case it wasn’t painfully obvious lol...
caption:
Amadeus’s Bday by krystalfan-2 I literally forgot how to draw my own characters, in case it wasn’t painfully obvious lol Amadeus’s birthday was yesterday, but I got started on this late. He’s the last one I will be doing!

Anyone else reuse their birthday or Christmas list for the other? I do, since my birthday is after Christmas. Makes it easier to make a list of what I want.
